def fibonacci(n):
    """
    This function calculates the n-th Fibonacci number recursively.

    Args:
    n (int): A positive integer.

    Returns:
    int: The n-th Fibonacci number.

    Time Complexity: O(2^n)
    Space Complexity: O(n)
    """
    if n < 1:
        return n
    else:
        return fibonacci(n - 1) + fibonacci(n - 2)
